## Serif / script location rule

> **Cormorant Garamond and Great Vibes may appear only in `components/website/` and
> `RunSheetDocument.tsx`. Nowhere else, at any size, for any reason.**

`components/website/` gets serif **and script** by Tier 3. The run sheet gets **Cormorant only,
on its print header only**, by the Tier 1 carve-out above. **Great Vibes never appears on the run
sheet.** The location rule is still a location rule — two locations, two justifications.

`--font-serif` and `--font-script` remain defined and loaded via `next/font/google` because
Tier 3 needs both (and the run sheet needs Cormorant). They must not be consumed outside the
locations above.

Fonts (target wiring):
- Figtree (400/500/600/800) → `--font-sans` (Tier 1 and Tier 2)
- Hanken Grotesk (400/500) → `--ws-font-sans` (**Tier 3 / `components/website/` only**)
- Cormorant Garamond (500/600) → `--font-serif` (Tier 3; Tier 1 print-header carve-out only)
- Great Vibes → `--font-script` (**Tier 3 only**)

Map all Tier 1 tokens into Tailwind (v4 `@theme inline`) in STYLE-01.

