## Tokens (target Soft stack — apply in STYLE-01)

```css
:root {
  --canvas: #F3EEF0;
  --surface: #FFFFFF;
  --well: #F7F3F5;
  --ink: #241C20;
  --muted: #857A80;
  --hairline: #EFE7EB;
  --ring: #DCD0D6;
  --accent: #C0396B;
  --accent-wash: #FBEEF3;
  --sage: #2F6B54;
  --clay: #B0762E;
  --clay-wash: #FBF1E2;
  --rosewood: #C4453F;
  --rosewood-wash: #FDECEB;
  --radius-card: 22px;
  --radius-inner: 14px;
  --radius-pill: 999px;
  --shadow-raised: 0 1px 2px rgba(60, 30, 45, 0.05),
    0 10px 30px -8px rgba(60, 30, 45, 0.11);
  --shadow-recessed: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(60, 30, 45, 0.06);
  /* Tier 2 emotional cards only */
  --card-shadow-emotional: 0 2px 4px rgba(70, 45, 52, 0.05),
    0 16px 40px rgba(70, 45, 52, 0.07);
}
```

**Live chrome values still in `app/globals.css` until STYLE-01** (for audit continuity; not the
target): `--canvas #FAF5EE`, `--ink #221A1D`, `--plum #7E3E57`, `--stone #E8DCCE`,
`--stone-soft #F1E8DD`, plus `--porcelain`, `--surface-2`, `--ink-soft`, `--ink-muted`,
`--plum-deep`, `--plum-tint`, `--rose`, `--radius` / `--radius-lg`, `--card-shadow`.

